lgp.core.environment.config

Class JsonConfigurationLoader.Builder

  • lgp.core.environment.config.JsonConfigurationLoader.Builder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentLoaderBuilder<TComponentLoader>
    Enclosing class:
    JsonConfigurationLoader

    public static class JsonConfigurationLoader.Builder
implements ComponentLoaderBuilder<TComponentLoader>

    A custom interface ComponentLoaderBuilder implementation for building a class JsonConfigurationLoader instance.

    The builder allows for a filename to be specified, which references a JSON file to load configuration data from.

    See Also:
    interface ComponentLoaderBuilder, class JsonConfigurationLoader
